Sentencas: LSCF/CGO composite cathodes decorated with small amount (less than 1 wt%) of nano CuO particles has been synthesized by infiltration technique.
Titulo: Improve the catalytic property of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3/Ce0.9Gd0.1O2 (LSCF/CGO) cathodes with CuO nanoparticles infiltration

Sentencas: The area specific resistance (ASR) of the LSCF/CGO at 500 degrees C has been significantly reduced by the CuO infiltration from 15.5 Omega cm(2) and 0.62 Omega cm(2) to 3.9 Omega cm(2) and 0.32 Omega cm(2) at 500 degrees C and 650 degrees C respectively.
Titulo: Improve the catalytic property of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3/Ce0.9Gd0.1O2 (LSCF/CGO) cathodes with CuO nanoparticles infiltration

Sentencas: The redox reaction of Cu2+/Cu1+ at the interface of CuO and LSCF/CGO has been assigned as the main reason for the improvement.
Titulo: Improve the catalytic property of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3/Ce0.9Gd0.1O2 (LSCF/CGO) cathodes with CuO nanoparticles infiltration

Sentencas: Lattice parameter change of LSCF at 500 degrees C has been detected by High Temperature XRD, indicating partial diffusion of Cu2+ into the lattice of LSCF, and formation of a new Cu containing compound.
Titulo: Improve the catalytic property of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3/Ce0.9Gd0.1O2 (LSCF/CGO) cathodes with CuO nanoparticles infiltration

Sentencas: The performance stability of the infiltrated samples has been investigated by aging at 500 degrees C and 650 degrees C for 150 hours in stagnant air.
Titulo: Improve the catalytic property of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3/Ce0.9Gd0.1O2 (LSCF/CGO) cathodes with CuO nanoparticles infiltration

Sentencas: A slight degradation of the catalytic property was observed during the aging process.
Titulo: Improve the catalytic property of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3/Ce0.9Gd0.1O2 (LSCF/CGO) cathodes with CuO nanoparticles infiltration

Sentencas: The degradation may be attributed to three factors: (i) the coarsening of CuO nanoparticles, (ii) segregation of the SrO due the lattice change and (iii) instability of the new Cu2+ contained compounds.
Titulo: Improve the catalytic property of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3/Ce0.9Gd0.1O2 (LSCF/CGO) cathodes with CuO nanoparticles infiltration
